elias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/01\/ummah-ilm-fiqh-hadith\/","url_meta":{"origin":39933,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: Allah guides people of Fiqh, Hadith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah will not let my nation agree upon misguidance. The hand of Allah is over the united community.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \"The interpretation of the united community, according to the scholars, are the people of Fiqh,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37995,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/07\/20\/ummah-three-disasters\/","url_meta":{"origin":39933,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: Allah protects the Muslims from three disasters","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 20, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Malik al-Ash\u2019ari reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has protected you from three calamities: that your Prophet supplicate against you and thus you all perish, that the people of falsehood prevail over the people of truth, and that you would unite\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18133,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/16\/every-bidah-is-misguidance-fire\/","url_meta":{"origin":39933,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Bid&#8217;ah: Every innovation is misguidance in Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 16, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn 'Abdillah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would praise Allah in his sermon, as He deserves to be praised, and then say, \u201cWhomever Allah guides, no one can lead him astray. Whomever Allah sends astray, no one can guide him. The truest word\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18160,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/17\/withdraw-from-misguidance\/","url_meta":{"origin":39933,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ruin: Withdraw from those leading Ummah astray","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe people will be ruined by a branch of the Quraysh tribe.\u201d They said, \u201cWhat do you command us to do?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIf only the people would withdraw from them.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3604,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42344,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/12\/06\/dajjal-imams-of-misguidance\/","url_meta":{"origin":39933,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dajjal: The Prophet fears Imams of Misguidance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 6, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: I said, \u201cO Messenge